{"tid":1636353,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(軍事分享)裝甲部隊於城鎮之弱點","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:45:03.000Z","uid":252670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc23101c74c4640e39faf872445f872e6d8fb7b","tid":1636353,"uid":252670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2xWyrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2xWyrL.jpg&h=0273645b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝甲部隊係空曠嘅地方當然係威係勢<br />\n但入到城市之後結果係點樣呢？<br />\n幻想一下四周圍都係高樓大廈<br />\n唔知係邊度伸個頭出嚟射支火箭炮<br />\n架坦克車就咁拜拜<br />\n所以<br />\n城鎮作戰必須要裝甲車同步兵互相協調<br />\n但係如果有人排曬陣列哂陣大模斯樣喺條街行<br />\n仲要冇遮冇掩<br />\n呢一班人嘅下場會係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純 學術討論 軍事迷<br />\n唔好扣帽子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58c0169746e26b82d90602214f290bda3e3c261","tid":1636353,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"坦克車入城？要空軍炸爛個城先安全"},{"pid":"2f6360bc5e03b7eaa0ea38fe776bf578a6debb39","tid":1636353,"uid":201212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇下車臣戰爭"}]}